    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Titles or names of works that are written, stamped, or printed on the work. For works of art, it may include any part of an inscription that is clearly intended by the creator or publisher to serve as a title or that the cataloging institution wishes to record as a title. For manuscript or book cataloging, it is the title on the title page or found elsewhere in the book.</Note_Text>
